### 5. cmd/activity.go â€” Update runActivityList scope display (around line 698-705)

Currently the `activity ls` command only reads `workScopeString`. Update to also handle `workScopeCel`. Replace the scope reading block (lines 697-705):
```go
scope := "-"
if ws, ok := e.Value["workScope"].(map[string]any); ok {
	wsType := mapStr(ws, "$type")
	if strings.HasSuffix(wsType, "#workScopeCel") {
		if labels, ok := ws["labels"].([]any); ok {
			var keys []string
			for _, l := range labels {
				if s, ok := l.(string); ok {
					keys = append(keys, s)
				}
			}
			scope = strings.Join(keys, ",")
		}
	} else if s := mapStr(ws, "scope"); s != "" {
		scope = s
	}
}
```

